11T07:55:35.000Z","msg":"做測試 political scale"},{"pid":"a3bc4d84b1b0047fb983f727f744556547c439b2","tid":1306355,"uid":158270,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d8795dc05bbf71cecb20320e5fb2925edb34ded5","tid":1306355,"uid":158270,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T07:55:35.000Z","msg":"做測試 political scale"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T07:55:56.000Z","msg":"Political spectrum *"},{"pid":"9a6d62b7e19945b3eb0d7bfa34e5e00e7fac01d3","tid":1306355,"uid":54344,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T08:22:28.000Z","msg":"左派右派從來都只係代表對立嘅理念，並冇一個解釋概括左右派嘅政治主張。<br />\n<br />\n左右喺經濟角度可以代表社會主義同資本主義<br />\n<br />\n亦都可以代表保守派同進步派，喺同性婚姻，墮胎，大麻合法化議題就係好好嘅例子，傳統保守嘅咪反對囉，反之。<br />\n<br />\n香港呢？傳統保皇黨就一定係左派？你睇下張宇人？簡直就係喺經濟方面企到最撚右，小政府，大市場，市場主導，廿蚊最低工資。<br />\n<br />\n李卓人張超雄唔係左派，姐係右派啦？非也，工黨呢啲以工人權益為先，仲唔係左派？<br />\n<br />\n大把例子講到出年都未完，左右之分，一直都只係二元對立嘅意識形態，並不能夠一碌鳩打一船人，左嘅就膠，右嘅就法西斯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5298615374cfbf34418942c350e8050ebf5b7850","tid":1306355,"uid":54344,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T08:26:01.000Z","msg":"左右只係將複雜嘅理念同主張簡化成兩邊，冇話一定要求要你揀一邊嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6d49410fb29eef63079044bf2606a8e7903635c6","tid":1306355,"uid":117744,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T09:18:47.000Z","msg":"好少見有人討論依個<br />\n其實左派嘅核心價值係<strong><ins><span style=\"color: red;\">平等</span></ins></strong>，<br />\n你試下將好多唔同左派嘅行動指標縱合一下，<br />\n就會發現點解要接收難民? 點解要講愛同和平? 點解要社會主義? 點解要行福利主義? 核心就係因為平等係佢地眼中最核心嘅價值。<br />\n<br />\n而相對於左派嘅平等黎講，右派比較強調<strong><ins><span style=\"color: red;\">自由</span></ins></strong>。<br />\n所以你會見到佢地係以保障本地利益為先，親疏有別。<br />\n點解要起幅牆擋住難民? 點解要行資本主義? 點解強調個人唔講集體?<br />\n<br />\n以上我都係執啲思想家嘅口水尾。<br />\n<br />\nBTW, 有時候好難一概而論分左右，咁樣分都係俾人簡單知道自己傾向邊一邊而已。"},{"pid":"421992dea9403e3e3199557edc396a3b885227c2","tid":1306355,"uid":203098,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T11:28:32.000Z","msg":"香港只有親中同反送中<br />\n冇左右派ge思想"},{"pid":"ede3eb66cedf1d3f453d99ea455a372539ea2d5e","tid":1306355,"uid":57677,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T11:49:05.000Z","msg":"呢度好多人以為自已右其實好撚左<br />\nor vice versa"},{"pid":"ab73441f2cbe7fcb554d249e5801b4486b738f9c","tid":1306355,"uid":160637,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T14:48:19.000Z","msg":"左追求平等 右認為點都有階級之別<br />\n左偏向革命、革新 右偏向維持既有制度"},{"pid":"fb019bdb0e53c3cfa5a7daaac42e897eaa7e5165","tid":1306355,"uid":137309,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T15:07:20.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"c02322e99d02748f059a7c70d3b472f7a37976a3","tid":1306355,"uid":58335,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T15:25:07.000Z","msg":"政右經左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"43635eb20ee3de8c2f9208324ee41b762ec8fc9e","tid":1306355,"uid":203098,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T15:26:04.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"9331fa8a0ed53b85bc2225cac6e4acdccde786b7","tid":1306355,"uid":70487,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T15:27:34.000Z","msg":"大部分連登人都係左派<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nfc from 一個月前政治光譜post"},{"pid":"ad667ab83d57341ccef683ca177205a76cbe8aa1","tid":1306355,"uid":160637,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T15:29:45.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.politicalcompass.org\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.politicalcompass.org&d=i5E3ds%2FeSPFE00WLmt8527%2FszHQdc4%2B4ddc640yZrNs%3D&h=549476b3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.politicalcompass.org</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8roBEST.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8roBEST.png&h=5cc630b7&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c5d042971699d7b34a0d997384defe47c3be1e6f","tid":